name: WHALE of a good time....
author: Benstartri
notes: It's a Whale deck, but I use Skreech. I love Skreech, wish I had a 3rd one. Made getting Whale out that much easier. CC was for mirror/specific cards and it came in clutch for some games.  Went from L2 to KOG with it, so it must be good right lol.
